      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 149.8205,
      "replayEndSec": 198.111981,
      "narrationText": "And finally rdc doctor for a local sanity check on your laptop. Node, SSH key, renet, Docker. All the things rdc itself depends on. That is the full series. From install to monitoring, all from your terminal.",
